import { Grid, Link, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

export const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{height: "30vh", backgroundColor: "#000", color: "#fff" }}>
        <Grid container >
            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Acerca de Nosotros</Typography>
                <Box sx={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "",margin: "1rem 0"}}>
                    <Link>Quiénes somos</Link>
                    <Link>Sala de prensa</Link>
                    <Link>Sostenibilidad</Link>
                </Box>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Información legal</Typography>


                <Typography>Términos de uso</Typography>
                <Typography>Conoce tus derechos</Typography>
                <Typography>Devolución de tasas de embarque</Typography>
                <Typography>Condiciones de contrato de transporte</Typography>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Explorar</Typography>

                <Typography>Prepara tu viaje</Typography>
                <Typography>Destinos</Typography>
                
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}
